Title: Config update: Site specific global settings are now also updated
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1614246996
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

During update from previous versions to Checkmk 2.0 some old global
configuration settings are rewritten. This is now also done in the site
specific global settings automatically during "omd update".
